OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough Law is likely to
OL,7,Freturn to Parliament before the summer
OL,8,Fbreak, David Lammy has said, as he
OL,9,Fcame under pressure to ensure the
OL,10,Fsecurity services were subject to its
OL,11,F"duty of candour".
OL,13,FThe Deputy Prime Minister told the
OL,14,FCommons that he was "confident" it
OL,15,Fwould be back before MPs in the next
OL,16,Fweek as he was asked about reports
OL,17,Fthat the MI5 had covered up for an
OL,18,Fagent who had attacked his girlfriend
OL,19,Fwith a machete and was "obsessed" with
OL,20,Fviolence.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@QO]vD@UOUvD@_O]{D@XOU{D@aO]
