OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat deputy leader Daisy
OL,7,FCooper said MI5 had given false
OL,8,Fevidence to courts to protect the
OL,9,Fagent, who has not been identified.
OL,11,FThe proposed law had previously
OL,12,Fstalled over concerns it would not
OL,13,Fapply to the intelligence agencies.
OL,15,FThe law, formally known as the Public
OL,16,FOffice (Accountability) Bill, will
OL,17,Frequire public officials to tell the
OL,18,Ftruth during inquiries and
OL,19,Finvestigations. It was promised by
OL,20,FLabour in its 2024 manifesto.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
