OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783682373
OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,FIt takes its name from the
OL,7,FHillsborough disaster in 1989 when 97
OL,8,FLiverpool fans were killed at the
OL,9,Ffootball stadium at Sheffield in a
OL,10,Fcrush during an FA Cup semi-final
OL,11,Fmatch.
OL,13,FIt was found afterwards that key
OL,14,Fpublic servants, including the police,
OL,15,Fhad not told the truth about the
OL,16,Fdecisions taken leading up to the
OL,17,Ffatal crush at the Leppings Lane end
OL,18,Fof the ground.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
