OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783682373
OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,FSpeaking during Prime Minister's
OL,7,FQuestions, Ms Cooper said: "MI5 has
OL,8,Fdefended in court an agent that they
OL,9,Fknew to be openly misogynistic,
OL,10,Fobsessed with violence and who used
OL,11,Fhis position to coercively control his
OL,12,Fgirlfriend Beth, and attack her with a
OL,13,Fmachete.
OL,15,F"To add insult to injury, MI5 also
OL,16,Fgave false evidence to the courts.
OL,26,@oD@\OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
