OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783682373
OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,F"So, will the Deputy Prime Minister
OL,7,Fuse this opportunity to offer Beth a
OL,8,Ffull apology on behalf of the
OL,9,FGovernment? And will he use his
OL,10,Fposition to bring back a full
OL,11,FHillsborough Bill next week to cover
OL,12,Fthe security services, so we can pass
OL,13,Fthe law before the summer recess?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
