PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783682373
OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,FMr Lammy, standing in for Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer during the Nato summit in
OL,8,FAnkara, responded: "She raises a very
OL,9,Fserious issue, of course, and I will
OL,10,Farrange for Beth to meet with the
OL,11,Fsecurity minister to discuss this in
OL,12,Fdetail. She also raises the
OL,13,FHillsborough Bill and I'm confident
OL,14,Fthat this will be before the House in
OL,15,Fthe coming days."
OL,17,FBoth Sir Keir, and Andy Burnham ` who
OL,18,Fis expected to be Labour's next leader
OL,19,F` have previously spoken of their
OL,20,Fsupport for the Bill.
OL,26,@pD@TOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
