OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783682373
OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'could return to
OL,4,CParliament in coming days'
OL,6,FIt was brought forward during the last
OL,7,Fparliamentary session and "carried
OL,8,Fover" to ensure it could pass after
OL,9,FParliament was prorogued.
OL,11,FIn 2025, the Government faced a row
OL,12,Fafter proposing amendments that would
OL,13,Fsee spies brought within the scope of
OL,14,Fthe law, but only with the approval of
OL,15,Fthe head of their services.
OL,17,FCampaigners warned this could be used
OL,18,Fas a way of escaping the new "duty of
OL,19,Fcandour" and the amendments were
OL,20,Fpulled.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@EO]zD@^OU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
